msgid ""
"Gamut Masks are a type of :ref:`resource <resource_management>`. As such, they can be saved, tagged, reordered and added to bundles. They are stored inside ``*.kgm`` files, which are ZIP files "
"consisting of a mimetype (:mimetype:`application/x-krita-gamutmask`), a preview.png and an SVG file describing the mask."
msgstr ""

